STATE
v.
Wali Farad Muhammad BILAL. No. 292P03-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 1, 2005. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Jeff Hunt, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 27th day of April 2005 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review under G.S. 7A-31:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 1st day of December 2005."
